Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（うめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（美世）私が やらなきゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}助け出す…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}絶対に！
